First Department,

April, 1952.

(April 30, 1952.) In the Matter of Michael J. Barry, Respondent, against John F. O’Connell et al., Individually and as Members of the State Liquor Authority, Appellants.

Motion transferred to the Appellate Division, Second Department, on the authority of Matter of Lacqua v. O’Connell, decided April 1, 1952 (280 App. Div. 31), for hearing and determination. Present — Peek, P. J., Callahan, Van Voorhis, Heffernan and Bergan, JJ.
